HEADWORD: Securipalp
<hw>Se*cu"ri*palp</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>securis</ets> ax, hatchet + E. <ets>palp</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of a family of beetles having the maxillary
palpi terminating in a hatchet-shaped joint.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Security</ent>⟦br⟧
